cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with remote sensing data and focuses on semantic segmentation of building footprints. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) to overcome missing and incomplete modalities, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which is a common theme in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with spatial data, which could fall under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves the integration of data acquired with different modalities, which could fall under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
